      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UBER IN (6) jumped $1.85F last start over 1200m at this track when third, beaten 2.5 lengths. Made ground and had presented off a Canberra Maiden win over this distance. Peaks and has the blinkers go on again. Deserves another chance. BRUTAL EYES (2) won here this grade/rip and then disappointed over 1400m on a heavy track at Nowra. Drops plenty in grade with a handy 3kg claim, and on a dryer surface is a decent chance to bounce. MILLY MOLLY MANDY (5) resumes for a Sydney barn off a Maiden win at Orange. Has had a soft trial but will need some luck from the awkward barrier. ROYALIFY (4) ran a better race last start to finish second at this track over 1200m. Should be in the finish again.",
